{"tid":1819434,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［正名］農曆新年的英文是什麼？","createTime":"2020-01-10T20:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T20:20:47.000Z","uid":85437,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6e29c62b0976e105f70ef01f6f968a72b3953e1a","tid":1819434,"uid":85437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T20:07:07.000Z","msg":"就快年初一<br />\n你會點樣用英文祝賀人地新年快樂？<br />\n我相信好多人都係寫Happy Chinese New Year<br />\n或者簡稱Happy CNY<br />\n<br />\n但農曆既新年唔係淨係Chinese先至會慶祝<br />\n亞洲好多地區都會慶祝<br />\n以月球黃道編曆既農曆 (Lunar) 一月初一<br />\n咁點解大家要將農曆新年局限比中國？<br />\n而且香港人過呢一個節日<br />\n係咪真係一定要同中國有關先？<br />\n韓國印尼新加坡等地方 個個都一齊過<br />\n連維基都寫&ldquo;generally referred to as Lunar New Year globally&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n初一 就一定係中國既初一嗎？<br />\n係咪樣樣野都可以比中國拎左個名？<br />\n所以我唔希望見到身邊既人再講Happy Chinese New Year<br />\n為農曆新年正名<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>Happy Lunar New Year</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人 唔好被農曆新年潛移默化<br />\n廣傳正確農曆觀念"},{"pid":"a04cf2e8ab6f78e6bd1f7e4a825a733057fef1be","tid":1819434,"uid":11598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T20:08:14.000Z","msg":"Gong Hei Fat Choi"},{"pid":"346af18bcfecc6d6d247c1c506fc24282a1590a5","tid":1819434,"uid":43178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T20:20:17.000Z","msg":"Happy Lunar New Year"},{"pid":"a0c7830820b1087b5d54fbdb0dc0c3745a964613","tid":1819434,"uid":315908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T20:20:47.000Z","msg":"下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家先知道有Chinese呢個字會係happy new year出現"}]}